What=E2=80=99s new with the Xaman Desktop App?

 Crossplatform compatibility
  Available on Windows, macOS, and Linux, ensuring broad accessibility acro=
ss devices.

 Browser flexibility
  Fully supported on Chromiumbased browsers, allowing for seamless integrat=
ion with your existing workflow.

 Improved interaction flow
  A desktopnative experience makes managing transactions, signing requests,=
 and interacting with decentralized applications more fluid and convenient.

 Enhanced productivity
  Ideal for users who prefer working on larger screens or need a more persi=
stent interface for frequent interactions.

Why move to desktop?

The desktop app is designed to complement your existing Xaman usage by prov=
iding:

 Faster navigation and multitasking
 A more stable environment for extended sessions
 Better visibility and control over your activities

Download and get started

To begin using the Xaman Desktop App, please download the latest version he=
re: https://www.xamandesktopclient.com/

After downloading:

1. Install the application for your operating system
2. Launch the app
3. Follow the setup instructions to connect and start interacting

We strongly recommend using the latest version of Xaman at all times to ben=
efit from the newest features, performance improvements, and important secu=
rity updates.

Your feedback matters

As this is the first release of the desktop app, there may be features that=
